						               													<description>You will be protagonist of a new and realistic Rugby Board Game where the different situations that this vibrant sport presents, are intertwined by means of smart charts. Fantail Rugby is an agile and dynamic Board Game that combines all the action of Rugby within the rules that govern. Fantail Rugby allows you to make (one or two) handed pass, line outs, scrums, kicks, tackles, mauls, rucks, tries, penalties and drops, besides other actions inherent to the Rugby Game. Fantail Rugby combines action, strategy and luck.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;About Fantail Rugby Board Game&amp;#10;Fantail Rugby is played by two coaches who must lead their teams to the victory. The smart charts are the soul of the game by having each of them a special design to be used according to game development. On the game board can clearly see the current situation of the game that is taking place in the smart chart in use, because the symbols of the board are in accordance with the symbols of the smart charts.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Attention:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;New updated version (2020) of the most entertaining and agile Rugby Game you have ever seen.&amp;#10;Now, smart cards have focused on an even more dynamic game by being designed to simulate a Seven Rugby Game . In addition, the images have been improved and the chances of reaching the try or a conversion are more common.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Teams can be made up of one player, two or three and the playing time is agreed in advance. The fact of being played with an eight-sided dice has a lot of random, but since smart cards have the possibility of deciding in various game situations, it gives to the same a touch of strategy which will depend on the score and the remaining playing time.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
